#, no-c-format
msgid "Sounds: Ludovic Grossard <email>ludovic.grossard@libertysurf.fr</email>"
msgstr "Sons: Ludovic Grossard <email>ludovic.grossard@libertysurf.fr</email>"

#. Tag: para
